The Argo NetCDF file format checker version 2.9.3 was released and activated on both US and Coriolis GDAC.  
This new version include (among other minor changes) the capacity to validate timeseries of technical data as described in the Argo User's Manual.

- [https://github.com/OneArgo/ArgoFormatChecker/releases/tag/v2.9.3](https://github.com/OneArgo/ArgoFormatChecker/releases/tag/v2.9.3){target="_blank"}
